Package org.forgerock.openam.sts.tokengeneration.state

Interface STSInstanceState<T extends STSInstanceConfig>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RestSTSInstanceState, SoapSTSInstanceState
    public interface STSInstanceState<T extends STSInstanceConfig>
    Interface which defines all of the state which the token generation service must be able to obtain from the state corresponding to a published STS instance.
